   ``We have married,'' said a brief announcement published Monday
in the marriage column of the Oslo newspaper Vaart Land. Vaart Land
and other Oslo newspapers said Harket's family refused comments.
They said Harket, 29, and Malmqvist, 25, have known each other for
two years and married on Feb. 4.
</TEXT>
