<TEXT>
   Esther Williams, former swimming champion who went on to star in
aqua-musical MGM movies like ``Million Dollar Mermaid'' and
``Neptune's Daughter,'' is diving into, what else, swimwear.
   ``I know what women look for in a bathing suit _ comfort,
